name: NEBUXEL - COMPUTING
description:
Fourth protagonist of the Nebuxel series, we present to you “computing”.
 
This subject, “computing”, represents the computing power that constantly supports and drives the metaverse. As a matter of fact, the latter already embodies an ultimate degree of power both within the economic and geopolitical fields but not only: in the short term, also Medicine and Diagnostics will also follow, strongly relying on this computational power.
 
So you can really say that whoever possesses more computing power in a certain sense has the upper hand and follows "computa et impera" as a general rule.
